==========================================================
WHAT IS NEXOTFE
==========================================================

NEXOTFE is a Premium Industrial ERP.

It was designed specifically for industrial companies that manufacture products, machines, equipment and engineering solutions.

It is NOT a generic ERP.

It is NOT an accounting system.

It is NOT a financial management platform.

Its primary focus is industrial operations.

==========================================================
WHO USES NEXOTFE
==========================================================

Typical customers include:

• Precision machining companies.

• CNC machining shops.

• Machine manufacturers.

• Industrial equipment manufacturers.

• Automation companies.

• Engineering companies.

• Industrial service providers.

• Custom manufacturing companies.

==========================================================
BUSINESS PHILOSOPHY
==========================================================

NEXOTFE was created with one principle:

Transform complex industrial processes into simple business decisions.

Every feature must contribute to this philosophy.

Complexity belongs inside the software.

Simplicity belongs to the user.

==========================================================
PROJECT PHILOSOPHY
==========================================================

NEXOTFE is built around real industrial workflows.

The system must represent how factories actually work.

The software must adapt to the business.

The business must never adapt to software limitations.

==========================================================
